    seasons: 'Nashville\'s free music scene is year-round but peaks in spring and fall with beautiful outdoor weather for the patios. Summer is hot, but Lower Broadway\'s air-conditioned honky-tonks keep the music going. CMA Fest in June floods the city with outdoor free stages on Broadway and the riverfront. Tin Pan South Songwriter Festival in spring features free rounds at various venues.',
