    seasons: 'Spring (April–June) and fall (September–October) are ideal for outdoor free music in Raleigh\'s mild Piedmont climate. The NCMA grounds programming runs spring through fall. Glenwood South and other bar districts are active year-round. Summer evenings bring outdoor concerts; winter drives the scene indoors to venues and breweries.',
